title: Spotfire developer
jobdescription:
Skills | Must-Haves:

* 5+ years of professional experience

* experience with Spotfire development and deployment process

* strong knowledge of Spotfire database models

* experience creating dashboards and reports in Spotfire using Iron Python, HTML, and CSS

* experience writing PL/SQL and Python for data analysis

* experience developing reports and dashboards in Power BI

* experience writing DAX expressions and Queries in Power BI


Nice to Have Skills:

* familiarity with BI governance practices

* knowledge of additional visualization tools (Tableau, Qlik)

* Bachelor's degree or above


Company | Job Insights:

* 1 opening

* 6-month contract, with potential extension

* hybrid position -- 3 days onsite/week in Houston, TX
